data.enText: the light brown nut of the walnut tree that has a rough surface and a hard round shell in two halves
the tree on which walnuts grow
the brown wood of the walnut tree, used in making furniture

tr: nut of any of various walnut trees having a wrinkled two-lobed seed with a hard shell
any of various trees of the genus Juglans
hard dark-brown wood of any of various walnut trees
used especially for furniture and paneling

value.def: Walnuts are edible nuts which have a wrinkled shape and a hard round shell that is light brown in colour.
A walnut tree or a walnut is a tree on which walnuts grow.

posc.def: Walnut is the wood of this tree.

example.ex: The stool comes in several sizes in walnut or mahogany.
example.tran: 凳子有几种尺寸，材质分胡桃木和红木两种。
